p.explain Easily add a heading container to your panel with
   span.btn-color .panel-header
   | . You may also include any
   span.btn-color
      code &lt;h1&gt;-&lt;h6&gt;
   | with a
   span.btn-color .panel-title
   | class to add a pre-styled heading.

